chart.name: Disk I/O
chart.programText:
A = data('^azure.vm.disk.ops.read.total').mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='A')
B = data('^azure.vm.disk.ops.write.total').mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='B')
C = data('^azure.vm.disk.io.write.total', rollup='average').mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='C')
D = data('^azure.vm.disk.io.read.total', rollup='average').mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='D')

chart.name: Network Bytes In vs 24hr Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('^azure.vm.network.io.receive.total', rollup='average').mean(by=['azure_resource_id', 'azure_resource_name']).publish(label='A')
B = (A).mean().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B/C-1).scale(100).publish(label='D')

chart.name: Top Virtual Machines by Bytes In
Network Bytes Out vs. 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('^azure.vm.network.io.transmit.total', rollup='average').sum().publish(label='A')
B = (A).mean().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B/C-1).scale(100).publish(label='D')

chart.name: Network Bytes Out vs 24hr Change %
chart.programText:
B = data('^azure.vm.network.io.transmit.total', filter=filter('primary_aggregation_type', 'true'), rollup='average').publish(label='B')
C = (B).mean().publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).timeshift('1d').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (C/D-1).scale(100).publish(label='E')

chart.name: Network Bytes Out
chart.programText:
A = data('^azure.vm.network.io.transmit.total', rollup='average').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Network Bytes In
chart.programText:
A = data('^azure.vm.network.io.receive.total', rollup='average').publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')
G = (A).max().publish(label='G')

chart.name: Network Bytes In vs. 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('^azure.vm.network.io.receive.total', rollup='average').sum().publish(label='A')
B = (A).mean().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B/C-1).scale(100).publish(label='D')
